### Test Sighting Reports Endpoints
### Estos son los nuevos endpoints de reportes para avistamientos

# Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7002/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Sighting Counts by Camera
GET {{baseUrl}}/sightings/reports/by-camera
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get Sighting Counts by Brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/sightings/reports/by-brand
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Sighting Counts by Engine Displacement
GET {{baseUrl}}/sightings/reports/by-engine-displacement
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

